OL,3,COpt-out testing finds 'significant'
OL,4,Clevels of HIV and Hepatitis in the
OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,FA groundbreaking opt-out blood testing
OL,8,Fprogramme has identified "significant
OL,9,Fnumbers" of people living with
OL,10,Fundiagnosed HIV and hepatitis in the
OL,11,FMidlands, ITV News Central can reveal.
OL,13,FThe testing initiative has been
OL,14,Fintroduced in the emergency
OL,15,Fdepartments of the Queen's Medical
OL,16,FCentre in Nottingham, Queen Elizabeth
OL,17,FHospital in Birmingham, New Cross
OL,18,FHospital in Wolverhampton, and Walsall
OL,19,FManor Hospital.
