OL,3,COpt-out testing finds 'significant'
OL,4,Clevels of HIV and Hepatitis in the
OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,FThousands of patients attending A&E at
OL,8,Fthese hospitals have been tested
OL,9,Funless they actively declined.
OL,11,FThe scheme, first launched by NHS
OL,12,FEngland two years ago in 33 A&E
OL,13,Fdepartments across cities such as
OL,14,FLondon, Manchester, Blackpool, and
OL,15,FBrighton, uncovered more than 4,000
OL,16,Fcases of undiagnosed blood-borne
OL,17,Fviruses.
