OL,3,COpt-out testing finds 'significant'
OL,4,Clevels of HIV and Hepatitis in the
OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,FAdditionally, it reconnected 5
OL,8,Fpatients living with HIV, 11 people
OL,9,Fwith hepatitis B, and 7 patients with
OL,10,Fhepatitis C to clinical services after
OL,11,Fthey had been lost to follow-up care.
OL,13,FThe programme aims to improve access
OL,14,Fto testing while reducing the stigma
OL,15,Fassociated with blood-borne viruses,
OL,16,Fultimately saving lives.
OL,18,FEarly diagnosis is key, as many people
OL,19,Fwith blood-borne viruses are unaware
OL,20,Fof their status until symptoms become
OL,21,Fsevere.
