OL,3,COpt-out testing finds 'significant'
OL,4,Clevels of HIV and Hepatitis in the
OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,FDr Ashini Fox, an HIV specialist at
OL,8,FNottingham University Hospitals NHS
OL,9,FTrust, said: "Opt-out testing in
OL,10,FEmergency Departments transforms
OL,11,Fpublic health by identifying
OL,12,Fundiagnosed cases of HIV, hepatitis B,
OL,13,Fand hepatitis C at the earliest
OL,14,Fopportunity, reducing transmission and
OL,15,Fimproving outcomes for individuals and
OL,16,Fcommunities alike."
