OL,4,Clevels of HIV and Hepatitis in the
OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,FBy making testing routine, it removes
OL,8,Fbarriers to diagnosis and ensures
OL,9,Fequitable access to care, addressing
OL,10,Fthe hidden epidemics of blood-borne
OL,11,Fviruses.
OL,13,F"These results are a testament to the
OL,14,Flife-changing potential of opt-out
OL,15,Ftesting," said Dr Steve Taylor
OL,16,FClinical lead for the opt out testing
OL,17,Fprogram at University Hospitals
OL,18,FBirmingham .
